entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="kor" o="이제 모든 희망이 사라졌어." t="This is it – all hope's lost now." b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="kor" o="어... 그래, 다음에 얘기하자." t="Uhh... OK, let's come back to this." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="그래... 알았어." t="Well... OK then." b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="kor" o="다시 올 줄 알았지." t="I knew you'd come back." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="빨리 결정해." t="Decisions, decisions." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="빨리 좀 하면 안 돼?" t="Can we pick up the pace?" b="" a=""/>
